{
  "stem": "2830.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about a man or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still didn't even believe that I'm free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I'm going to go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where do you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have nobody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No place-- where you wind up?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, he said, he's a dentist, he's got to go back to Poland to liquidate his office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The equipment, that's to sell, or what, and he's moving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wanted me to go with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't want to leave me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he told the woman, the what she gave out the rations and everything in that block, you know, all the people were living, to keep an eye on me and everything.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, he said, when he met my husband, OK, he said, don't you dare ever talk to this-- you know--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- no, to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I shouldn't talk to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, he's not for real, he's just that and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said he didn't agree anything, anything my husband said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He disagreed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a-- you know-- a settled, a dentist, a mature person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was only-- how old was my husband?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's only two years older than I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he's 22.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, you know-- and then he lived through the war and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he didn't mature, yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- he said-- And he left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember, like now, that he just grabbed me, this Herman-- I have pictures of him-- to go with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said we're going to go, and he was going to liquidate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wouldn't leave me because he knew that he was going to leave me with George.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, he's gone, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, he's going to keep in touch.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
